Text:
This is the last one in the series. Bit of a pity.
Scott has moved on to other things.

I have tried to upload these files but it's taking forever. Thanks to those that have been patient.
you can also view the footage at http://www.scottgillen.com/ if you can't wait any longer.
I will leave them up until they have all been uploaded totally.
Just be warned that there is two scott gillen web sites. the other one is a wanky dance club site.
